# Instagram Performance Analytics for Sugar Cosmetics

This project provides a complete social media analytics report of **Sugar Cosmetics' Instagram** performance using Power BI / Tableau.  
It includes KPI dashboards, engagement insights, top-performing posts, hashtag analysis, and strategic recommendations for boosting marketing performance.

---

## ðŸš€ Project Objectives

- Analyze engagement (Likes, Comments, Saves, Shares)
- Identify monthly posting trends and high-performing content
- Compare post formats: Image, Video, Carousel
- Study hashtag performance and weekday trends
- Build an interactive dashboard using Power BI / Tableau
- Provide strategy recommendations for social media growth

