## ðŸŽ¯ Business Insights (Summary)

- Reels generate higher engagement than images.
- Tutorials, product demos, and how-to posts receive more saves.
- Weekdays (Tueâ€“Fri) show the strongest engagement.
- Hashtags related to trends and product categories help improve reach.

---

## ðŸ“Œ Recommendations

- Increase Reel posting frequency  
- Use trending audio + 8â€“12 targeted hashtags  
- Improve CTA-based captions  
- Collaborate with influencers & makeup creators  
- Schedule posts on high-engagement days  
- Focus on save-worthy educational content  

